        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Rove says the first question strategists need to ask their candidates is, ‚ÄúWhy are you running?‚Äù I.e, what do they offer to voters? It‚Äôs a fine starting point.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
