            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "David Axelrod is enchanted with focus groups, comparing them to group therapy. You herd people with free time into a temporary office, force them to answer questions like, ‚ÄúIf the candidates were animals, what kind of animal would they be?‚Äù And ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "boom, ",
            "type": "text",
